
SHOUT(2)                   silmul_efun                   SHOUT(2)

名稱
     shout - 對所有線上的玩家顯示指定的訊息

語法
     varargs void shout(string msg, mixed exclude);

描述
     This simul_efun displays the string "msg" to everyone in the
     mud  except  the  speaker  and (optionally) anyone listed in
     "exclude". The "exclude" argument may be either an object or
     an  array  of  objects,  or  the  argument  may  be  omitted
     entirely.

其它參考檔案
     /adm/simul_efun/shout.c

作者
     Ichabod@TMI, 3/10/93
     wade@future 4/8/1996 翻譯

MudOS Release 0.9         Last change:                   3-19-93

